/Models/
*.mlmodel
*.mlpackage
*.gguf
*.bin
.me

# #832/#913 PR8: the on-device output-safety classifier is COMMITTED (founder
# decision: embed, never download). Re-include this one .mlpackage + its inner
# model.mlmodel / weight.bin, overriding the broad model globs above. Largest
# inner file is ~43 MB (< GitHub's 100 MB per-file limit), so normal git.
!Sources/EnviousWisprLLM/Resources/OutputClassifier.mlpackage/
!Sources/EnviousWisprLLM/Resources/OutputClassifier.mlpackage/**

